===Noun===
'''south'''

# One of the four major [[compass point]]s, specifically 180°, directed toward the [[South Pole]], and conventionally [[downwards]] on a map.
# The [[down]] or [[negative]] direction.
#:''His luck turned '''south'''.''
# (physics) The [[negative]] or [[south pole]] of a [[magnet]], which seeks geographic south although attracted to a magnetic [[north pole]].

